# Implement File-Map Builder (Supabase ‚Üí AgentFS)

## What
Create a service that builds the AgentFS file tree from our data sources (Supabase, StarRocks schemas, static files).

## Why
The AgentFS needs to be populated with our semantic layer before the agent can use it. This builder:
1. Fetches current schema metadata from StarRocks
2. Loads OKR/P&L configurations from Supabase
3. Applies user-level RLS to filter what's visible
4. Materializes everything as AgentFS files

## Implementation Pattern

```typescript
// lib/infra/agentfs-builder.ts

